## Exit Criteria (Per Feature)

- [ ] Unit tests for core business logic (TDD workflow followed)
- [ ] Integration tests for API endpoints
- [ ] E2E tests for P0 user flows — happy + error path (Playwright POM pattern)
- [ ] Visual QA passed — no Critical/High visual bugs
- [ ] All tests passing
- [ ] Coverage >= 80% (aspire to 100% where AI cost is near-zero)
- [ ] TEST_PLAN.md updated
- [ ] No flaky tests
- [ ] Verification-loop report generated and attached to G4 review
